<div class="flysas modal open" id="confirm-flight" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="modal-title" data-onload="false">
  {{#if widgetCss}}<style>{{{widgetCss}}}</style>{{/if}}
  <div class="modal-content">
    <h1 id="modal-title" class="h2 modal-title">Please confirm change of flight</h1>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-close" data-close="true" aria-label="Close Modal">
      <svg class="sas-icon sas-icon-in--close" role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" id="in--close" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><rect width="24" height="24" rx="4"></rect><g fill="currentColor"><path id="eka" d="M14.149 11.972l4.528 4.528-2.122 2.121-4.527-4.527L7.5 18.62 5.379 16.5l4.527-4.528L5.38 7.445 7.5 5.323l4.528 4.528 4.527-4.528 2.122 2.122-4.528 4.527z"></path></g></g></svg>
    </button>
    <p>Change flight means your original flight will be cancelled and replaced by the new one. This applies to all passengers in the booking.</p>
    <div class="modal-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-lg btn-no" data-close="true">Close first modal</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{#if widgetJs}}<script>{{{widgetJs}}}</script>{{/if}}
</div>
